{
  "stem": "8786.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were all sentenced to death.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But they were killing them and we could even hear that the shots.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when I was running for these flowers, for these [HUNGARIAN], and they were shooting at us, even for picking up a little grass, which is usually given to horses.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They didn't want this [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Germans didn't want it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I will never forget another thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Once I was standing and there was a German SS standing like this, with his open legs and his boots.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And beneath, under his legs, I've seen over there a piece of rotten tomato peel.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I put my little finger there and tried to grab it out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he sees it and just boom.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "With his big boots, he just stepped on it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So it wasn't the question that they didn't have what to give us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They had so much food, after the liberation less than a half a mile from the camp in Gunskirchen, we found over there warehouses where the macaronis and cans of meat.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They were so deep.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Tens of thousands of cans of meat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "All right, they were horse meat, whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Sugar.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "People were dying because they did not watch themselves and they were overeating themselves.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "This is a well-known fact, but that is already after the whole circus was over.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But we were talking about our march from Malthausen to Gunskirchen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "This was three days.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I would say one third of those people who were marching through those roads-- probably, maybe not one third, but hundreds of boys were killed on the road.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we did find snails and we put a little can and somebody put a little fire and somehow tried to cook it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Who has the patience to wait for it cooks?",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
